WEBVTT

00:06:59.252 --> 00:07:03.506
Wealth is generated by accumulating
resources in one generation

00:07:03.530 --> 00:07:07.148
and transferring them
to subsequent generations.

00:07:07.649 --> 00:07:11.376
Median white household wealth

00:07:11.400 --> 00:07:14.465
is 147,000 dollars.

00:07:15.307 --> 00:07:18.228
Median Black household wealth

00:07:19.419 --> 00:07:21.990
is four thousand dollars.

00:07:22.506 --> 00:07:25.641
How do you explain this growing gap?

00:07:26.776 --> 00:07:27.926
Hard history.

00:07:28.665 --> 00:07:32.380
My great-great-grandfather
was born enslaved